Fix to allow sending large messages via the bridge between two or more HornetQ servers
=======================================================================================
1.  Download HornetQ-2.1.2 Final source from http://anonsvn.jboss.org/repos/hornetq/tags/HornetQ_2_1_2_Final/

2.  Update the source for BridgeImpl.java located in
  <base install>/src/main/org/hornetq/core/server/cluster/impl/

3.  Build the distribution

  cd <base install>/src
  ./build.sh

4.  Update the hornetq-2.1.2 Final jars hosted by TorqueBox 1.0.x

    ruby script for step #4 is hornetq-deploy.rb
